      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GENTLE SPARK (1) found the going tougher but ran well to place over 365m at this track (20.89) in Grade 5. Won an easier race the start before that at this track. Good form should continue. DESI'S DREAM (3) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (19.47) in a Grade 5 at Bulli. Leading chance. WESTBURN HARADA (5) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.5 lengths away in third (22.80) behind Sabini at Bulli. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Overdue and is among the main hopes. PAPA GUISEPPE (2) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.",
